---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import headshotImage from '../assets/images/site/engates_john.jpg';
---

<Layout title={`About - ${config.title}`} description="AI Researcher & Technology Innovator with 30+ years of experience">
	<section class="about-header">
		<h1>About John Engates</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">AI Researcher & Technology Innovator</p>
	</section>

	<article class="about-content">
		<div class="profile-section">
			<Image 
				src={headshotImage} 
				alt="John Engates - Professional headshot" 
				class="headshot"
				width={400}
				height={400}
				format="webp"
				quality={90}
			/>
			<div class="download-links">
				<a href={headshotImage.src} download class="download-btn">
					Download Headshot
				</a>
				<a href="/John_Engates_Speaker_Bio.txt" download class="download-btn">
					Download Speaker Bio
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="bio-section">
			<h2>Current Focus</h2>
			<p>{config.author.bio}</p>

			<h2>Professional Journey</h2>
			
			<div class="timeline">
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<h3>Field Chief Technology Officer - Cloudflare</h3>
					<span class="timeline-date">2021 - 2025</span>
					<p>Leading global Field CTO organization, guiding enterprises through AI and security transformations. Focusing on Zero Trust architectures, SASE solutions, and helping organizations prepare for the post-quantum era.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<h3>Client Chief Technology Officer - NTT Global Networks</h3>
					<span class="timeline-date">2018 - 2020</span>
					<p>Led technology strategy and client engagements for one of the world's largest telecommunications companies, bridging the gap between complex network infrastructure and business value.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<h3>Chief Technology Officer - Rackspace Technology</h3>
					<span class="timeline-date">2002 - 2018</span>
					<p>18-year journey from employee #35 to CTO, helping grow the company from startup to over $2 billion in annual revenue. Created the Intensive Hosting division that supported Internet giants including YouTube in its early days. Pioneered "Fanatical Support" culture that became an industry standard. Led the company through IPO and established Rackspace as a leader in managed cloud services.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<h3>Founder & General Manager - Internet Direct</h3>
					<span class="timeline-date">1995 - 2000</span>
					<p>Founded one of Texas's first Internet Service Providers, growing to over 10,000 customers in the San Antonio area. This early entrepreneurial experience laid the foundation for understanding how to scale Internet infrastructure.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2>Major Achievements & Contributions</h2>
			<ul class="achievements-list">
				<li><strong>Healthcare.gov Crisis Response (2013)</strong> - Called to the White House to help rescue the failing website during a critical national healthcare rollout</li>
				<li><strong>Congressional Testimony</strong> - Testified before the U.S. House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform on cloud computing's strategic value for government</li>
				<li><strong>OpenStack Co-founder</strong> - Led creation of the distributed storage system that became OpenStack Swift, now powering some of the world's largest storage platforms</li>
				<li><strong>Open Compute Project Board Member</strong> - Helped "open source cloud computing hardware" as one of the founding board members, democratizing data center innovation</li>
				<li><strong>Board Leadership</strong> - Currently serving on boards of Frost Bank (NYSE: CFR) and James Avery Craftsman Jewelry</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Awards & Recognition</h2>
			<ul class="achievements-list">
				<li><strong>UTSA Alumnus of the Year</strong> - University of Texas at San Antonio (2014)</li>
				<li><strong>CTO of the Year</strong> - San Antonio Business Journal Tech Titans Award (2014)</li>
				<li><strong>Top 50 Influencers in Cybersecurity</strong> - CIO Magazine</li>
				<li><strong>Cloudflare Innovator Award</strong> - For excellence in cybersecurity strategy</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Current Research</h2>
			<p>My current research explores the emergent behaviors and collective intelligence that arise when AI agents work together: a natural evolution from decades spent building the distributed systems that connect our world. I'm passionate about the transformative potential of multi-agent systems and their applications in reshaping how we work, create, and innovate.</p>

			<h2>Speaking & Mentorship</h2>
			<p>Throughout my career, I've been the translator between complex technology and business value, whether speaking at global conferences, advising boards, or mentoring the next generation through TechStars. I remain connected to UTSA through the College of Sciences Advancement Council and continue as an early-stage investor in cloud and SaaS startups.</p>

			<h2>Beyond Tech</h2>
			<p>I split my time between Texas (where I work) and Colorado (where I play), finding inspiration in both the tech ecosystems and mountain landscapes. When not pushing the boundaries of AI, you'll find me off-roading, cycling, snowboarding, or capturing it all through my photography.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="contact-section">
			<h2>Connect With Me</h2>
			<ul class="social-links">
				{config.social.linkedin && (
					<li><a href={config.social.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a></li>
				)}
				{config.social.twitter && (
					<li><a href={config.social.twitter} target="_blank" rel="noopener">X (Twitter)</a></li>
				)}
				{config.social.github && (
					<li><a href={config.social.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
				)}
				{config.social.email && (
					<li><a href={`mailto:${config.social.email}`}>Email</a></li>
				)}
			</ul>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6) 0;
		border-bottom: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.profile-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
	}

	.headshot {
		max-width: 400px;
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.download-links {
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		display: flex;
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.download-btn {
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit)) calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 4px;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.download-btn:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-text-primary);
		text-decoration: none;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.bio-section h2 {
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.bio-section p {
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.achievements-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
	}

	.achievements-list li {
		padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.achievements-list li::before {
		content: 'â–ª';
		position: absolute;
		left: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}

	.timeline {
		margin: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4) 0;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
		padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 5);
		position: relative;
	}

	.timeline-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -8px;
		top: 0;
		width: 13px;
		height: 13px;
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		border-radius: 50%;
		border: 3px solid var(--color-background);
	}

	.timeline-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
		color: var(--color-text-primary);
	}

	.timeline-date {
		display: inline-block;
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
	}

	.timeline-item p {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.contact-section {
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.social-links {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
		justify-content: center;
		margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
	}

	.social-links a {
		font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		padding: calc(var(--grid-unit)) calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
		display: inline-block;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}

	.social-links a:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-background);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.headshot {
			max-width: 300px;
		}
	}
</style>